    <abstract>
      <t>Some functionalities (e.g., fragmentation/reassembly and Encapsulating Security Payload) provided by IPv6 can be viewed as delivery functions independent of IPv6 or even IP entirely. This document proposes to provide those functionalities at different layers (e.g., MPLS, BIER or even Ethernet) independent of IP.</t>
